script.name: plugin.guilds.soverview.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] $sector = $a.obj -> get sector $sector = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get sector $table.stations = $sector ->get factory table from sector @ $data = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getdata : Sector=$sector Station Table=null Asteroid Table=null Existing Table=$table.stations Cycle Time=36000 gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input end
return null
sub.BuildMenu: $cycle.time = $data[0] $table.products = $data[1] $table.resources = $data[2] $table.surplus = $data[3] $table.needed = $data[4]
$do.cycle.time = 3600 $lines = 5 $menu = create custom menu array
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=705 $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$table.products gosub sub.DrawWare
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=708 $exclude.table = $table.products $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$table.resources gosub sub.DrawWare
set menu option: $menu, maximum menu height=$lines lines set menu option: $menu, no select lines=[TRUE] set menu option: $menu, remove main header=[TRUE] set menu option: $menu, icon=78 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge]
$sector = $a.obj -> get sector $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3400 $input = create input: id='guilds.soverview' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$sector callback=null endsub
sub.DrawHeading: $text.cols = array alloc: size=5 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$heading $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2013 $text = create custom menu column string, position=250 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3401 $text = create custom menu column string, position=350 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2015 $read.text = 'Surplus' $text = create custom menu column string, position=450 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2014 $text = create custom menu column string, position=550 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols endsub
sub.DrawWare: gosub sub.DrawHeading $drawn = 0 if $sorted.array $size = size of array $sorted.array $i = 0 while $i < $size $ware = $sorted.array[$i] inc $i =
if $exclude.table do if $exclude.table[$ware] continue end
$text.cols = array alloc: size=5 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=250 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text $value = $table.products[$ware] gosub sub.ConvertValue $text = create custom menu column string, position=250 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $value = $table.resources[$ware] gosub sub.ConvertValue $text = create custom menu column string, position=350 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text $value = $table.surplus[$ware] gosub sub.ConvertValue $text = create custom menu column string, position=450 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[3] = $text $value = $table.needed[$ware] gosub sub.ConvertValue $text = create custom menu column string, position=550 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols inc $drawn = end end
if $drawn $lines = $lines + $drawn else inc $lines = $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end endsub
sub.ConvertValue: if $value if $do.cycle.time $tmp = $value * 100 $value = fixed multiply and divide: $tmp * $do.cycle.time / $cycle.time $value.1 = ( $value / 100 ) * 100 $value.2 = $value - $value.1 $value.1 = $value.1 / 100 $text = convert number $value.1 to string if $value.2 < 10 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s.0%s', $text, $value.2, null, null, null else $text = sprintf: fmt='%s.%s', $text, $value.2, null, null, null end else $text = convert number $value to string end else $text = '-' end endsub
return null
